{"tid":1049070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港人免費乖搭360昂坪纜車","createTime":"2019-03-06T04:34:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T15:41:28.000Z","uid":73340,"like":461,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":94,"replies":[{"pid":"046cb3ae98ec2f99bca9b1910a633c400433f110","tid":1049070,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T04:34:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190306/mobile/bkn-20190306110303382-0306_00822_001.html?eventPath=hk_news&amp;eventID=402882b15cbe4d9c015ccf249b9b1ac3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190306%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190306110303382-0306_00822_001.html%3FeventPath%3Dhk_news%26eventID%3D402882b15cbe4d9c015ccf249b9b1ac3&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhWVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=66005afc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190306/mobile/bkn-20190306110303382-0306_00822_001.html?eventPath=hk_news&amp;eventID=402882b15cbe4d9c015ccf249b9b1ac3</a><br />\n<br />\n昂坪360昨(5日)宣布推出「港人感恩月」，香港身份證號碼有「3」、「6」、「0」其中兩個數字的港人，可逢每年的3月與6月免費乘搭來回昂坪纜車標準車廂，但原來該纜車於今個月6至26日因保養維護，即本月只餘5天可提供免費纜車優惠。大批網民嬲爆今早(6日)在昂坪360 Facebook專頁留言「無心搞唔好搞啦！」昂坪360接受東網查詢後急補鑊，表示會延長3月的優惠期至4月10日，而今年6月不會有定期維修<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n玩弄香港人就有份"},{"pid":"47e289536e71ad055557d640c497b268e01be42b","tid":1049070,"uid":9193,"like":309,"dislike":8,"score":301,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T04:37:14.000Z","msg":"你服務對象都唔係香港人啦 扮乜嘢啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfb5ec3d2df25213f4af68b6d2862bfa99f9e661","tid":1049070,"uid":39177,"like":574,"dislike":3,"score":571,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T04:39:34.000Z","msg":"要幾乖先搭得?"},{"pid":"21be2965e5fd13e76b6d88e666edb755356523a4","tid":1049070,"uid"